---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
import "../../styles/services/accounting.css";
---

<Layout>
  <main class="service-page accounting-page">
    <section class="service-page-hero">
      <div class="service-page-shell">
        <p class="service-page-eyebrow">accounting</p>
        <h1>Clear books. Better decisions.</h1>
        <p class="service-page-lead">
          Good accounting should do more than record what already happened. We
          help business owners maintain reliable records, understand their
          financial position, and make decisions with better information.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="service-page-intro">
      <div class="service-page-shell service-page-two-column">
        <div>
          <p class="service-page-kicker">How we help</p>
          <h2>Accounting that supports the business</h2>
        </div>
        <p>
          Every business needs accurate records, but the right level of support
          varies. Some clients need ongoing bookkeeping and reporting. Others
          need cleanup work, QuickBooks guidance, or year-end assistance. We
          start with what you actually need and build from there.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="service-page-offerings">
      <div class="service-page-shell">
        <div class="service-page-section-heading">
          <p class="service-page-kicker">Services</p>
          <h2>Support built around what you need.</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="service-page-grid">
          <article class="service-page-offering">
            <h3>Bookkeeping and reporting</h3>
            <p>
              Consistent monthly or quarterly accounting with financial
              statements that are useful, not just produced.
            </p>
          </article>
          <article class="service-page-offering">
            <h3>QuickBooks support</h3>
            <p>
              Setup, cleanup, troubleshooting, and practical guidance for
              QuickBooks Online and related workflows.
            </p>
          </article>
          <article class="service-page-offering">
            <h3>Catch-up and cleanup work</h3>
            <p>
              Help bringing incomplete or inaccurate records up to date before
              tax filing, financing, or a business decision.
            </p>
          </article>
          <article class="service-page-offering">
            <h3>Year-end accounting</h3>
            <p>
              Review and adjustment of records so the books are ready for tax
              preparation and financial reporting.
            </p>
          </article>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="service-page-questions">
      <div class="service-page-shell service-page-two-column">
        <div>
          <p class="service-page-kicker">Common questions</p>
          <h2>Start with the question in front of you.</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="service-page-question-list">
          <article class="service-page-question">
            <h3>How often should my books be updated?</h3>
            <p>
              That depends on the business. Monthly accounting is usually best
              when you need timely reporting, while simpler businesses may only
              need quarterly support.
            </p>
          </article>
          <article class="service-page-question">
            <h3>Can you clean up prior periods?</h3>
            <p>
              Yes. We can review the existing file, identify what needs
              correction, and establish a cleaner process going forward.
            </p>
          </article>
          <article class="service-page-question">
            <h3>Do I have to use QuickBooks Online?</h3>
            <p>
              No. We recommend the platform that fits the work, but QuickBooks
              Online is often the most practical long-term choice for small
              businesses.
            </p>
          </article>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="service-page-cta">
      <div class="service-page-shell service-page-cta-inner">
        <div>
          <p class="service-page-kicker">Let's talk</p>
          <h2>Need help with accounting?</h2>
          <p>
            Tell us what you are working through. We will help you determine the
            next practical step.
          </p>
        </div>
        <a href="/contact">Contact Us</a>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>
